<?php
return ['messages'=>['<p>1. What was EJI’s purpose behind the JGA 2025 booth concept?<br /><br />At <strong>JGA 2025</strong>, we chose to focus on <strong>purpose and people</strong> over showcasing our jewellery creations. Our goal was to highlight <strong>emerging talents</strong>, offering them a distinguished platform to share their creativity and engage directly with the industry. This initiative reflects our ongoing commitment to <strong>corporate social responsibility</strong>, <strong>innovation</strong>, and <strong>nurturing the next generation</strong> of jewellery professionals.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>2. Who were the student designers featured at the EJI booth?<br /><br />We proudly featured a group of talented <strong>jewellery design students</strong> from <strong>Hong Kong Design Institute (HKDI)</strong> and <strong>Young College – Pro-Act Jewellery</strong>. Each student brought their own unique style, story, and perspective, contributing to a total different yet very inspiring jewellery showcase around the show floor.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>3. How is EJI supporting young talent in the jewellery industry long-term?<br /><br />EJI is committed to <strong>empowering the next generation</strong> through meaningful exposure, and long-term opportunities. Beyond our initiative at JGA 2025, we continue to build bridges between generations by offering <strong>creative art workshops </strong>for children of various age groups. Our vision is to help shape a more inclusive, sustainable future for the industry.</p>'=>'<p>1. EJI 在 JGA 2025 展位背後的概念是什麼？<br><br>在 <strong>JGA 2025</strong>，我們選擇聚焦於<strong>目標與人</strong>，而非展示我們的珠寶創作。目標是突出<strong>新一代人才</strong>，為他們提供一個卓越的平台分享創意並直接與行業互動。這一計劃反映了我們對<strong>企業社會責任</strong>、<strong>創新</strong>及<strong>培育下一代</strong>珠寶專業人士的持續承諾。  </p>
<p> </p>
<p>2. EJI 展位上那些學生設計師是誰？<br><br>他們是來自<strong>香港設計學院（HKDI）</strong>與<strong>Pro-Act 珠寶學院</strong>的一群才華橫溢的<strong>珠寶設計學生</strong>。每位學生帶來了獨特的風格、故事和視角，為展會注入截然不同的元素。 </p>
<p> </p>
<p>3. EJI 如何長期支持珠寶行業的年輕人才？<br><br>EJI 持續通過為不同年齡的兒童提供<strong>創意藝術工作坊</strong>，<strong>培育下一代</strong>。我們的願景是塑造一個更具包容性、可持續的珠寶行業未來。  </p>','<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>Designed by</em> <strong>CHAN, Ying Sum</strong><br /></span></p><div><div><div><p>SHAPE - BA (Hons) Jewellery, Materials and Design <span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier">|</span> HKDI Jewellery</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/clearjewelry_sc/#">@clearjewelry_sc</a></strong></p></div></div>'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>設計：</em><strong>CHAN, Ying Sum</strong><br></span></p><div><div><div><p>SHAPE – 珠寶、材料與設計榮譽學士 <span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier">|</span> HKDI</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/clearjewelry_sc/#">@clearjewelry_sc</a></strong></p></div></div>','<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>Designed by</em> <strong>NG, Chun Fan</strong><br /></span></p><div><p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier"><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none">Higher Diploma in Jewellery Design and Technology </span>|</span> HKDI Jewellery</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/frankie_jy/#">@frankie_jy</a></strong></p>'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>設計：</em> <strong>NG, Chun Fan</strong><br></span></p><div><p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier"><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none">Higher Diploma in Jewellery Design and Technology </span>|</span> HKDI</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/frankie_jy/#">@frankie_jy</a></strong></p>','<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>Designed by</em> <strong>SIU, Wing Ki</strong><br /></span></p><div><p>SHAPE - BA (Hons) Jewellery, Materials and Design <span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier">|</span> HKDI Jewellery</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/kakudo._.official/#">@kakudo._.official</a></strong></p>'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>設計：</em> <strong>SIU, Wing Ki</strong><br></span></p><div><p>SHAPE – 珠寶、材料與設計榮譽學士 <span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier">|</span> HKDI</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/kakudo._.official/#">@kakudo._.official</a></strong></p>','<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>Designed by</em> <strong>YEUNG, Hoi Kiu Melody</strong><br /></span></p><div><p>SHAPE - BA (Hons) Jewellery, Materials and Design <span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier">|</span> HKDI Jewellery</p><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/sagitts.jewelry/#">@sagitts.jewelry</a></strong></p></div>'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>設計：</em> <strong>YEUNG, Hoi Kiu Melody</strong><br></span></p><div><p>SHAPE – 珠寶、材料與設計榮譽學士 <span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier">|</span> HKDI</p><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/sagitts.jewelry/#">@sagitts.jewelry</a></strong></p></div>','<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>Designed by</em><strong> CHUNG, Ka Chun</strong><br /></span></p><div><div><div><div><p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier"><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none">Higher Diploma in Jewellery Design and Technology </span>|</span> HKDI Jewellery</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/jewellery_tinnnn/#">@jewellery_tinnnn</a></strong></p><p> </p></div></div></div>'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>設計：</em><strong> CHUNG, Ka Chun</strong><br></span></p><div><div><div><div><p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier"><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none">珠寶設計與技術高級文憑 </span>|</span> HKDI</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/jewellery_tinnnn/#">@jewellery_tinnnn</a></strong></p><p> </p></div></div></div>','<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>Designed by <br /></em><strong>LEE, </strong></span><strong>Hoi Ying</strong>, <br /><strong>LAM, </strong><strong>Kwai Tung</strong>,<br /><strong>LEE, Wai Kiu</strong> &amp; <br /><strong>TONG, Wan Yiu</strong> </p><p>Pro-Act Jewellery <span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier"> | Young College</span></p><div> </div>'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>設計：<br></em><strong>LEE, </strong></span><strong>Hoi Ying</strong>, <br><strong>LAM, </strong><strong>Kwai Tung</strong>,<br><strong>LEE, Wai Kiu</strong> &amp; <br><strong>TONG, Wan Yiu</strong> </p><p>Pro-Act 珠寶 <span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier">| 青年學院</span></p><div> </div>','<p>At EJI, social corporate responsibility is not a checklist – it’s our core value. As a responsible jewellery manufacturer, we are deeply committed to nurturing new talent, championing creativity, and building a dignified and sustainable future for the jewellery industry</p><p>Our initiative at JGA 2025 marks just the beginning of this journey. And we invite you to walk alongside us as we continue to empower, engage and build what comes next. Let’s shine together.</p>'=>'<p>對 EJI而言，企業社會責任不是一份清單——它是我們的核心價值。作為負責任的珠寶製造商，我們致力於培育新人才、推廣創意，為珠寶行業打造可持續未來。 </p><p>我們在 JGA 2025 的計劃僅是這一旅程的開始。我們邀請您與我們同行，繼續賦能、互動並共創未來，一起發光。  </p>','<p>At this year’s <a href="https://jga.exhibitions.jewellerynet.com/"><strong>Jewellery &amp; Gem Asia Hong Kong (JGA) 2025</strong></a>, we made a subtle yet significant shift. Not just our positioning on the show floor, but in our perspective.</p><p>We asked ourselves a simple but radical question: <br />“What if a trade fair booth wasn’t about showcasing what we’ve created – but what we believe in?”</p><p>So we set aside the traditional business approach to a B2B jewellery exhibition:<br />No commercials products.<br />No new launches.<br />No business agenda.</p><p>Instead, we embraced a bold idea: to hand over the spotlight to the <strong>next generation of talents</strong>, and to spark a conversation about the future of jewellery industry.</p><p>The result? A space that drew visitors to stop by our booth with surprise, curiosity, and engagement.</p>'=>'<p>今年的六月<a href="https://jga.exhibitions.jewellerynet.com/"><strong>香港珠寶首飾展覽會（JGA 2025）</strong></a>，EJI帶來了微妙但意義深遠的轉變。 </p><p>我們問了自己一個簡單卻大膽的問題：<br>「若珠寶展位展示的並非產品，而是我們的信念，會是怎樣？」</p><p>於是，EJI摒棄了傳統 B2B 珠寶展的商業模式：<br>沒有商業產品。<br>沒有新品發布。<br>沒有會議流程。</p><p>取而代之，我們實行了一個創新做法：將聚光燈交給<strong>下一代人才</strong>。</p><p>結果，一個吸引訪客駐足、充滿驚喜、好奇和互動的空間應運而生。 </p>','<p>From the very beginning, we knew this would challenge expectations.<br /><br />Our space at JGA this year wasn’t built to attract buyers <br />– it was designed to spark genuine connection, and to shift the spotlight away from us, <br />toward something more meaningful.<br /><br />With the open layout and the oversized glowing letters of our name, the space felt different because it <strong><em>was</em></strong> different. <br /><br />It wasn’t a PR stunt. <br />We didn’t pitch a story. <br />We simply showed up with a purpose <br />– to express our belief in the future of the jewellery industry.</p>'=>'<p>從一開始我們就知道這決定充滿挑戰。<br><br>這次的展位非為吸引買家而設計——然而，它是個促進連結的空間。<br><br>並將焦點從我們身上，轉到更有意義的方向。<br><br>開放式佈局、醒目發光的超大字母名稱，形成<strong><em>獨特</em></strong>的空間。<br><br>這並非公關噱頭。<br>沒有推銷故事，只有目標——表達我們對珠寶行業未來的信念。</p>','<p>To all who stopped by – to ask, to share, or just to listen – thank you. You made this space come alive. Your presence gave these students something powerful:</p><p>A sense of recognition and belonging in the industry.</p><p>And in return, they reminded us of all of what the jewellery can truly dbe: meaningful, inclusive, and full of potential.</p>'=>'<p>謝謝所有駐足的人，無論是提問、分享，還是聆聽，你們都讓這個空間充滿了生命力，給了學生們強大的支持——  </p><p>一種行業認可與歸屬感。</p><p>同時，學生們亦提醒了我們珠寶真正的力量：充滿意義與包容性，潛力無限。</p>','<p>We stepped back - to let them step forward.<br />And they did.</p>
<p>Not just with their stunning creations, but with their insights, their energy, their courage, and their dreams. They brought the real sparkle.</p>
<p>Over four days at JGA, what unfolded was far more powerful than we had imagined. It became a space where generations connected, where ideas were exchanged. The students soaked in the real business world experience, engaged with professionals, and – perhaps for the first time – felt what it means to belong in the jewellery industry.</p>
<p>Their sparkle wasn’t in gemstones. It was in imagination, courage, and vision.</p>'=>'<p>我們暫時退後——讓他們大步前行。<br>而他們做到了。</p>
<p>那些耀眼的創作，懷抱了學生們的想法、能量、勇氣和夢想。他們帶來了真正的光芒。 </p>
<p>這4天展現的成果遠超想像。我們的展位成為一個世代交匯、思想交流的空間。學生們有機會與專業人士互動，體驗真實的商界，感受屬於珠寶行業的歸屬感。  </p>
<p>他們的光芒源於想像力、勇氣和遠見；比寶石更耀眼。 </p>','A Different Kind of Presence'=>'與眾不同的存在','A Quiet Shift Spoke Loudly'=>'全新面貌 重大改變','At the heart of this initiative was a group of passionate jewellery design students from Hong Kong Design Institution (HKDI) and Young College – Pro-Act Jewellery.'=>'這計劃的核心，是一群來自香港設計學院（HKDI）與Pro-Act 珠寶青年學院、充滿熱情的珠寶設計學生。','Empower. Engage. Build the Future.'=>'賦予、互動、共創未來  ','Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)'=>'常見問題 (FAQ)','Letting the Next Generation Shine'=>'讓下一代發光發熱','Photo Credit: Informa Markets Hong Kong'=>'照片：Informa Markets Hong Kong','Thank you – For Making This Matter'=>'感謝每一位，讓一切充滿意義','The Stunning Jewellery Pieces'=>'令人驚艷的珠寶作品','Watch the Full Video'=>'觀看影片','caption-image-ba8a09b'=>'照片：Informa Markets Hong Kong','dailymotion_url-video-29b49b8'=>'https://www.dailymotion.com/video/x6tqhqb','editor-text-editor-140bf9c'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>設計：</em> <strong>NG, Chun Fan</strong><br></span></p><div><p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier"><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none">Higher Diploma in Jewellery Design and Technology </span>|</span> HKDI</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/frankie_jy/#">@frankie_jy</a></strong></p>','editor-text-editor-21da0df'=>'<p>從一開始我們就知道這決定充滿挑戰。<br><br>這次的展位非為吸引買家而設計——然而，它是個促進連結的空間。<br><br>並將焦點從我們身上，轉到更有意義的方向。<br><br>開放式佈局、醒目發光的超大字母名稱，形成<strong><em>獨特</em></strong>的空間。<br><br>這並非公關噱頭。<br>沒有推銷故事，只有目標——表達我們對珠寶行業未來的信念。</p>','editor-text-editor-398eaf2'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>設計：</em> <strong>SIU, Wing Ki</strong><br></span></p><div><p>SHAPE – 珠寶、材料與設計榮